<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>School Notice Board  St Francis Girls Suwerwa</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,600;0,800;1,600&family=Lora:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <link rel='stylesheet' href='/high.css'/>


  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css"/></head>
<body>


<%- include('../layout/header-simple', { navActive: 'aboutUs' }) %>


<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="index.html">SFGS</a> <span>/</span> Information <span>/</span> School Notice Board</div>
    <h2>School <em>Notice Board</em></h2>
    <div class="hero-divider"></div>
    <p class="hero-tagline">Official announcements, term dates, fee reminders, and important administrative information.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<div class="motto-strip">
  <span class="star"></span>
  <p>Stay Informed  Stay Ahead</p>
  <span class="star"></span>
</div>
<div class="main-wrap">
  <main class="content">
<p>The SFGS Notice Board is the primary channel for official announcements affecting students, parents, and staff. From term dates and fee reminders to school events and important administrative notices  check here regularly to stay informed.</p>

<h2 class="section-heading">Current Notices</h2>
<div class="notice-list">
<% if (!notices.length) { %>
  <p>No notices have been posted yet.</p>
<% } %>
<% notices.forEach(function (n, i) { var d = new Date(n.created_at); %>
<div class="notice-item<%= i === 0 ? ' pinned' : '' %>">
  <div class="notice-date-block"><div class="day"><%= d.toLocaleDateString('en-GB', { day: '2-digit' }) %></div><div class="month"><%= d.toLocaleDateString('en-GB', { month: 'short' }) %></div><div class="year"><%= d.getFullYear() %></div></div>
  <div class="notice-body"><span class="notice-tag"><%= n.category %></span><% if (n.is_urgent) { %><span class="pinned-icon"></span><% } %><h3 style="margin-top:.5rem"><%= n.title %></h3><p><%= n.content %></p></div>
</div>
<% }); %>
</div>

<div class="term-dates-banner">
  <div>
    <h3> Looking for Term Dates?</h3>
    <p>View the full school calendar for the academic year, including opening dates, half-term breaks, and closing days.</p>
  </div>
  <a href="highterms.html" target="_blank">View Term Dates</a>
</div>
</main>
  <aside class="sidebar">
<div class="sidebar-card">
  <div class="sidebar-card-header"><h4>Information Desk</h4></div>
  <div class="sidebar-card-body"><a class="sidebar-link" href="Snews.html">News and Events <span class="arrow"></span></a><a class="sidebar-link active" href="noticeboard.html">School Notice Board <span class="arrow"></span></a><a class="sidebar-link" href="games".html">Games &amp; Sports <span class="arrow"></span></a><a class="sidebar-link" href="clubs".html">Clubs &amp; Societies <span class="arrow"></span></a><a class="sidebar-link" href="leadership.html">Student Leadership <span class="arrow"></span></a><a class="sidebar-link" href="facilities.html">Facilities &amp; Amenities <span class="arrow"></span></a></div>
</div>
<div class="apply-cta">
  <h4>Applications Open</h4>
  <p>Join one of Kenya's most prestigious schools. Applications are now being accepted.</p>
  <a class="apply-btn" href="https://www.sfgsuwerwa.sc.ke/application" target="_blank">How to Apply </a>
</div>
</aside>
</div>


<%- include('../layout/footer') %>
<%- include('../layout/sticky-toggle') %>
</body>
</html>
